<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Schedule (Automatic)</title>
    <style>
        /* stolen from 15A Universal Styles */
        body {
            background-color:#1A1A1A;
            background-image: url("https://www.101011010.com/img/bg_tile_1.gif");
            color:white;
            margin:16px;
            line-height: 1.4;
            /* font-family: "MS PGothic", serif, enable_if_you_want; */
        }

        a {
            font-size: x-large;
        }

        a:link {
            color:#00F0FF; /* this is more readable on a dark dark background and (as a bonus) looks nicer! */
        }
        a:visited {
            color: #00F0FF;
        }
        a:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        a:active {
            color: #00F0FF;
        }

        .text {
            /* width: 80%; */
            max-width: 800px;
            text-align: justify;
            text-justify: newspaper;
        }

        :root {
            --margin-left: 48px;
            --margin-top: 28px;
            --block-width: 796px;
        }

        .banner {
            width:75%;
            background-color: #931d1d;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-left: var(--margin-left);
            margin-top: var(--margin-top);
            max-width: var(--block-width);
            border-color: #444444;
            border-width: 2px;
            border-style: ridge;
        }

        .zzbanner {
            width:75%;
            background-color: #2554C7 ;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-left: var(--margin-left);
            margin-top: var(--margin-top);
            max-width: var(--block-width);
            border-color: #444444;
            border-width: 2px;
            border-style: ridge;
        }

        .block {
            background-color: #2b3032;
            width:75%;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-left: var(--margin-left);
            margin-top: var(--margin-top);
            max-width: var(--block-width);
            border-color: #444444;
            border-width: 2px;
            border-style: ridge;
        }
        .sched_day_tmr {
             background-color: #357968;
             width:50%;
             margin: 2em;
             padding: 1em;
         }
        .sched_day_datmr {
            background-color: #5b140b;
            /* colour theory, ignore this this is just for testing
            background-color: #6a4823;
            background-color: #296a33;
            background-color: #2f6a5f;
            background-color: #29556a;
            background-color: #3d386a;
            background-color: #6a3a62;
            background-color: #6a2c32;
            background-color: #56617a;
            background-color: #549ac6;
            background-color: #c68252;
            */
            width:50%;
            margin: 2em;
            padding: 1em;
        }
        .special {
            background-color: rgba(60, 60, 80, 0.5);
            margin: 0.5em;
            padding-left: 0.5em;
            padding-right: 0.5em;
            padding-top: 0.2em;
            padding-bottom: 0.3em;
        }
        .onl {
            animation: blink 1.2s ease infinite;
        }
        @keyframes blink{
            0%{
                opacity: 1;
            }
            50%{
                opacity: 0.4;
            }
            100%{
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
        .bleh {
            color:#999999;
        }
        .greeting {
            opacity: 75%;
        }
        li:nth-child(5) {
            opacity: 56.666%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<h2>Hello and welcome to the automatic schedule webpage!</h2>
<h4>スケジュールのページへいらっしゃいませ‼</h4>
<div class="text">
    <b>Brief statistics section:</b><br/>
    <span class="bleh">Days remaining in the school year:</span> {{stat.days_rem}} <span class="bleh">(that's </span>{{stat.days_rem_pct}}% <span class="bleh">complete)<br/>
    Ped / holidays (excluding christmas etc) remaining: </span>{{stat.ped_rem}} <span class="bleh">(</span>{{stat.ped_past}} <span class="bleh">already happened)</span><br/>
    That's it, have a nice day! <i> (calculated in {{stat.time_ms}}ms) </i><br/>
    <br/>
    (1 more thing - if there is a mistake / something that should be added ; just lmk and i'll fix it.)
</div>



{% if show_banner == 1 %}
<div class="banner">
    <h3>automatic notice: it's close to the start/end of the day, so the date is about to change, or maybe just did. don't get confused. look at the date. thanks.</h3>
</div>
{% endif %}

{% if show_banner == 2 %}
<div class="zzbanner">
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="4">
        <tr>
            <td><img height="40px" src="https://101011010.com/schedimg/zzz.gif" alt="(zzz)"/></td>
            <td><h3 >
                notice: it's pretty late. you should probably get some sleep. thanks for checking the schedule though :) now gn.
            </h3></td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>
{% endif %}

{% for block in blocks %}
<div class="block" style="background-color: {{block.bgcolorcode}}">
    <h3>
        {{block.title}} ({{block.date}}) {% if block.is_over == true %} was {% else %} is {% endif %}
        <b>{{block.day_str}}</b>{# {% if block.is_online == true %}<span class="onl"> ONLINE</span>{% endif %} #}.
    </h3>

    {% if block.is_over == true %}
    <h4 class="onl">This day has already happened, at least in terms of school.</h4>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.classes_is_some == true %}
    <p>This day's classes are:</p>
    <ol>
        {% for class in block.classes %}
            <li>{{class}}</li>
        {% endfor %}
    </ol>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.special_is_some == true %}
    <div class="special">
    <p><em>Special events!</em></p>
    <ul>
        {% for event in block.special %}
            <li>{{event}}</li>
        {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
    <p class="greeting">{{block.greeting}}</p>
</div>
{% endfor %}

<br />
<br />
<br />

<a class="nexta" href="?count={{nextcount}}">Click here to load more days!</a>
<br />
<br />
<p>bonus points: this page was generated in <i>{{benchmark_duration_ms}}ms.</i> ({{benchmark_stat_pct}}% of that is generating top stats)</p>
<em>thanks for checking in! ur awesome</em>
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />

</body>
</html>
